snippet.title: Digimon World DS [#1]  -  New World (no commentary)
snippet.description:
Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLAb0kV9EaRfkmTsB2255fi6-pp4SrVTxl
My Digimon World DS: Favors Side Quests Guide - https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLAb0kV9EaRfmP4FSGfGeqkgG-XTeDsJ6s

English version of "Digimon World DS" Walkthrough on Nintendo DS emulator. No commentary. No random encounters. Leveling is done "behind the scenes". Follow my Digimon Tamer adventures!

Game description: 

In the game, the player assumes a role of Digimon tamer and embarks on an exciting journey to discover, raise, train and command over 230 unique Digimons.You build Digi-Farms to raise, evolve and communicate with your Digimons.
